                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-304-18770305 t18770305-304-punishment-39"></join>Seven Years' Penal Servitude.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The two sovereigns were ordered to be given to the Prosecutor.</hi>
